{"tid":94333,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"小雞問母雞： 為什麼人類都有名字，而我們全都叫雞？","createTime":"2017-01-25T06:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T11:50:57.000Z","uid":25981,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5759c18fe1f7073f0769ad7a1583aee6e3b92b95","tid":94333,"uid":25981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:53:45.000Z","msg":"小雞問母雞： 為什麼人類都有名字，而我們全都叫雞？ <br />\n母雞回答： 人類活著的時候都有名字，但死了也全都叫鬼了。 我們活著的時候沒有名字，但死就有很多名字了！ <br />\n小雞說： 真的嗎，都叫些什麼名字？ <br />\n母雞說： 咖喱雞、白切雞、香菇雞、燒雞、炸雞、烤雞、手撕雞、口水雞、辣子雞、醬油雞、鹽焗雞、沙薑雞、童子雞&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5500fbb7d7453ff85fefa3fea5f6718eea74f4a5","tid":94333,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:54:58.000Z","msg":"小學雞"},{"pid":"e98032269f6ddabe57ec85d0a2a5c8c11d21b11b","tid":94333,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:55:02.000Z","msg":"雖然聽過但都俾個LIKE你~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e296331354f70eaf1b9c9685e3e49736ef491d48","tid":94333,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:20:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學雞</blockquote><br />\n小學雞"},{"pid":"2896fded5606fb73f7001dd44cf53576a661b4a1","tid":94333,"uid":25981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c6d37c759c284356639fad011e9709d73c5416","tid":94333,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:33:43.000Z","msg":"咁計既話，豬都係喎，燒豬，乳豬，飛天少女豬事丁。。。。"},{"pid":"a8886b20aeb1aae9c954310e5a688db32afe0cfc","tid":94333,"uid":19301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim